          "value": ""
        },
        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "Player killing is allowed here. If you are of Good alignment you may slay those of Evil alignment and vise versa. However rampant, mindless player killing will not be tolerated and you will be banned for life. Neutral alignment must Roleplay out a reason for slaying an alignment. Do not make a habit of killing those of much lower level or you Will be banned."
          }
        }
      },
