        },
        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "Your Alignment matters here. If you are of Good alignment the Free Peoples of Middle Earth have allied to fight the power of Sauron. These havens and cities are where you can seek refuge. If you are of Evil alignment you serve Sauron the Dark Lord of Mordor. Places that ally with Sauron will be your refuge. If you choose to walk the middle ground... There are several neutral cities open to you as well as Evil and Good."
          }
        }
      },
      {
