        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "The entire city of Minas Tirith has been put in and there are several merchants that reside therein. Much of Mordor has been added, such as Barad Dûr and the Black Gate. Many areas have been added south of Lothlorien... Wold, Nindalf, Dagorlad, and the Dead Marshes. Some additional Good cities have also been added. Such as: Helm's Deep, Henneth Annun, and The Wood of Greenleaves home of Legolas."
